    "#creating dataset in time series for LSTM model \n",
    "#X[100,120,140,160,180] : Y[200]\n",
    "def create_ds(dataset,step): ## dataset=ds_train(692),step=timestamp(100)\n",
    "    Xtrain, Ytrain = [], []\n",
    "    for i in range(len(dataset)-step-1): ## 692-100-1=591\n",
    "        a = dataset[i:(i+step), 0] ##  - ds_train[0:100,0]\n",
    "        Xtrain.append(a) ## x_train=0\n",
    "        Ytrain.append(dataset[i + step, 0]) ## y_train=100\n",
    "    return np.array(Xtrain), np.array(Ytrain)"
   ]
